    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击杀敌人，即可进化成敌人形态，玩家将操控拥有此能力的变异生物，不断和其他变异生物厮杀，进化成更为强大的生物，在恐怖的外星人实验中存活下来，成为异兽之王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特点：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进化自由，只要击杀敌人，即可进化成敌人形态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/e2304af8edab97b47baaaeb6cfb156c8.avif?t=1756684571\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras_big/e2304af8edab97b47baaaeb6cfb156c8.avif?t=1756684571 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >危机四伏，外星人的实验场会潜伏着各种危险，玩家需要时刻保持警惕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/c9a9ef2aea1c19c93e0d4d0cd1a1ecf4.avif?t=1756684571\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras_big/c9a9ef2aea1c19c93e0d4d0cd1a1ecf4.avif?t=1756684571 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸体验，风格宏大独特的外星实验场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/0c70ca054a4093ea6e53223038b0e4aa.avif?t=1756684571\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras_big/0c70ca054a4093ea6e53223038b0e4aa.avif?t=1756684571 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特性多样，变异生物都拥有独特的能力，提取并搭配不同的特性，打造独一无二的异兽之王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/a6c489f9001e05a731ffb931279bb838.avif?t=1756684571\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras_big/a6c489f9001e05a731ffb931279bb838.avif?t=1756684571 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斗智斗勇，想击杀强大的变异生物，直接挑战并不是最好的办法，需要合理借助实验场机关和其他变异生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/1545e31a69005c680405473e812e9b80.avif?t=1756684571\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras_big/1545e31a69005c680405473e812e9b80.avif?t=1756684571 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >限时生存，随着时间推移，会有越来越强大的实验体加入厮杀，生存到最后才能成为异兽之王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/79ef70d535502eea62322a6daf5388d6.avif?t=1756684571\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras_big/79ef70d535502eea62322a6daf5388d6.avif?t=1756684571 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
